name: Membership 2011/12
description:
Membership benefits include:

- Discounted training sessions in the pool.
- Discounts at numerous outdoor equipment retailers.
- A space to store your own boat/paddles in our secure stores.
- The ability to attend our many and awesome trips!

name: An MUCC Pleasure Cruise, Destination; Great Langdale Beck
description:
This is going to be a lovely trip that almost everyone will be capable of taking on, paddling through what is tipped as England's most beautiful valley!

Great for those of you that might be up for a more relaxing trip at this point, or anyone who wants to do some unconventional sightseeing, how delightful!

There's also some optional more exciting bits on the river too, so really you're getting the best of both worlds! A great river to tick off then!

This will be the last MUCC river trip of this semester, so make sure you get on it before the long, boring Christmas holidays without any paddling come along ;P

Matimus

name: The AU Christmas Ball 2011!
description:
The Ball is going to be held at The Palace Hotel this year, on Sunday the 11th of December. It's always a great end to the year before we all head off for the Christmas Holidays, and it'll be straight after the next Liverpool Docks polo tournament, so what better way to celebrate us winning? ;P

Tickets include a bucks fizz reception, 3 course meal, half a bottle of wine and of course the best party of the year!

It will be a black tie event, so we'll all look presentable (for once!)

Email Nick & Polly if you have any questions;
